snippet.title: Hmph! Hmph! Yowai - Trailer
snippet.description:
Hmph! Hmph! Yowai is a Singleplayer Guild Battle Action RPG. Playing as a guildmaster in an open world fantasy setting, you need to recruit NPC guild members and construct your guild base to challenge and defend against other guilds. Your goal is to defeat nine other guilds and become the top guild.

Wishlist the game on steam!
=============================================================
Steam Store : https://store.steampowered.com/app/2848310/Hmph_Hmph_Yowai/
=============================================================
